    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This specification defines how a series of Security Event Tokens (SETs) can be delivered to an intended recipient using HTTP POST over TLS initiated as a poll by the recipient.  The specification also defines how delivery can be assured, subject to the SET Recipient's need for assurance.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
